node.js build on google's v8 engine
only js applcn which connects to database
js - cannot connect to database...api is used to connect with database
node 
npm - to install packages...package for bootstrap,angular,typescript...etc
whenever we install node, npm comes along with it
REPL -> Read Eval Print Loop 
REPL commands : ctrl+c : stop
                .save : save the session
packgae.json -> containes all dependencies

two types to create
npm init -> creates pckage.json(ask questions)
npm init --yes -> creates without any questions

//first set values
npm set init-license 'MIT'
npm set init-author-name "bhanu"
//then initialize the values
npm init --yes

//to get author name
npm config get init-author-name
(or) npm get init-author-name
//to delete license
npm config delete init-license

npm init --yes -> every time we modify , run it

npm install 'name'
npm uninstall 'name'

